{"tid":2492772,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"點解有啲人總係覺得越貴越好？","createTime":"2021-04-17T11:09:19.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-17T11:39:40.000Z","uid":383193,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"7928452da8318c0fb6a835a59254e8f08248e1e8","tid":2492772,"uid":383193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T11:09:19.000Z","msg":"阿媽包咗啲麵返嚟，同我講「嗱，好貴㗎，周圍侍應都話好正」（咁佢作為餐廳嘅侍應，唔通話自己餐廳嘅野難食咩）。佢個麵包含麵、菇、同花膠：啲麵太多汁，食落嘅好感好奇怪，而且有少少鹼味；啲花膠冇咩味，口感都好奇怪；菇正常少少，但係菇味太重。總而言之，成碟野好難食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>係嘅，有時個質同個價係正相關嘅，但係唔好因此將價錢當唯一嘅衡量標準好唔好？重視下自己個感受，唔好人云亦云，有返啲判斷力好唔好？</strong>"},{"pid":"4976b1486f3ca4c1e3b54c6cd4aeddd78cc8177e","tid":2492772,"uid":124400,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T11:28:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 樓主份人係咪唔講得笑"},{"pid":"73a3d06eaeaffee437ce059ad41f2234a2d05f25","tid":2492772,"uid":54557,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4976b1486f3ca4c1e3b54c6cd4aeddd78cc8177e","tid":2492772,"uid":124400,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T11:28:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 樓主份人係咪唔講得笑"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T11:32:58.000Z","msg":"似係，同佢普普通通講一句嘢都咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c111cc4a1679878172cdf87c8ab60b06e6728512","tid":2492772,"uid":16719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T11:38:12.000Z","msg":"你咪試下大快活扒好食啲定米芝蓮餐廳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"958fd2c6c5a9198fac6453b0dc66acd693bbcd7c","tid":2492772,"uid":395000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T11:39:40.000Z","msg":"阿媽見到d人話好食<br />\n所以覺得你會鍾意食<br />\n先特登留比你食姐<br />\n咁撚認真<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}